yumm how to make peanut butter and chocolate pie easy quick recipes please thanks chocolate peanut butter pie c butter softened oz semi sweet chocolate melted and cooled eggs c confectioners' sugar c peanut butter smooth not chunky c heavy cream baked inch pie shell beat eggs with cup of the butter the melted chocolate and the sugar for full minutes until smooth and thick in separate bowl beat peanut butter with remaining cup of butter while beating add cup of the cream to make the peanut butter of spreadable consistency that will swirl into chocolate mixture spoon chocolate mixture into pie shell swirl peanut butter into chocolate mixture beat remaining heavy cream until thick spread on top of pie refrigerate until served Chocolate Ice cream Peanut butter Cold Stone Creamery Butter Pancake Confectionery Japanese cuisine Cake Tofu Bread Cookie Tea Cuisine of Denmark Pie Cheesecake Cuisine of the Philippines Coffee Chili con carne M&M's Cocoa Maple syrup Kit Kat Dairy Peanut Baked Alaska Soup Pizza Jewish cuisine Oreo Chocolate Salty Balls Sandwich French toast Cuisine of the Southern United States Kraft Dinner Potato Cuisine of the United States Halva French cuisine Casting Cream (food) Milk Souffl__ Tamale Idli Biscuit In-N-Out Burger Heath bar Recipe Peruvian cuisine Barbecue Peanut butter and jelly sandwich Ramen Cajun cuisine The J.M. Smucker Co. Mayonnaise Alice B. Toklas brownie D__ner kebab Dumpling Mango Dim sum Mince pie Girl Scout cookies Cuisine of Brazil Turkish Delight Rice Krispies Sushi Custard Cha chaan teng Yoghurt Apple pie Marshmallow Gatorade Bacon Vegetarian cuisine Soap Philadelphia, Pennsylvania Milkshake Cuisine of Malaysia Pea soup Bengali cuisine Food Rice pudding Yoplait Jam French fries McDonald's Microwave oven Hot chocolate Cuisine of Canada Potato chips 